<!-- Services -->
<div id="services" class="services ha-waypoint" data-animate-down="ha-header-small" data-animate-up="ha-header-large">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <div class=" container TitleSection">
                    <header class="page-head">
                        <h1>
                            Who we <small> are</small>
                        </h1>
                    </header>
                </div>

                <div class="story-para">
                    <p>Frustrated with expensive local printers for your customized t-shirt needs? Cheap t shirt printing with unparalleled quality is a click away with CustomInk. You can design your own t-shirt with ease - our Virtual Lab makes it a snap to use your own artwork, creating and ordering your tshirts in just minutes. Our Lab gives you the ability to preview what your screen printed t-shirt will look like, and our service team is available seven days a week to help you; they'll even make suggestions on how to keep your order costs down. An expert artist reviews every order, ensuring that your t shirt screen printing looks awesome. We offer a money-back guarantee, and our standard free shipping means your order will arrive within 14 days. We have a rush service with delivery in 7 days.</p>
                    <p>Designing your own tshirts is easy and fast with CustomInk. And, if you've never ordered custom clothing on the Internet before, not to worry. We've got t shirt printing down to a science, while preserving your art.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="ser_wrap_3">
                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="icon_ser"><i class="fa fa-briefcase"></i></div>
                                    <div class="wrap">
                                        <h3>Print your pictures</h3>
                                        <p>We do retail printing. You may send us your pictures and choose a shirt type and color to print on. The average cost is 25 euros.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="icon_ser"><i class="fa fa-camera"></i></div>
                                    <div class="wrap">
                                        <h3>Deliver orders</h3>
                                        <p>We provide timely-fasioned delivery of your orders to home. In Bratislava we gurantee delivering in 3 days since you order recieved. Delivering to other locations is accomplished by post.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-4 hidden-xs hidden-sm">
                            <img src="~/images/TradeMark.gif" alt="slider" asp-append-version="true" style="max-width: 500px; width: 100%; height: auto; " />
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-sm-6">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="icon_ser icon_ser-right"><i class="fa fa-comments"></i></div>
                                    <div class="wrap wrap-right">
                                        <h3>Design amazing prints</h3>
                                        <p>We are passioned on fitting in people moods and have a solid experience in designing amazing prints. We print on different shirts: T-Shirts, Svitshots and Hoodies. In addition, we use cloth of different colors and type: cotton, lycra.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <div class="icon_ser icon_ser-right"><i class="fa fa-dashboard"></i></div>
                                    <div class="wrap wrap-right">
                                        <h3>Supply bulks</h3>
                                        <p>We supply printed shirts in bulks to retailers, starting from 10 shirts. The discount for 50 shirts is 5%, for 100 - 10%, for 200+ - 15%.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
